search_results.title: Bio - Mia Kankimäki — Author
search_results.snippet: Mia Kankimäki (b. 1971) is a Finnish author. Her two best-selling books blend travelogue, memoir, biography and women's history.

search_results.title: M.I.A. | Biography, Music, & Facts
search_results.snippet: MIA (born July 18, 1975, London, England) is a British-born Sri Lankan rapper who achieved global fame with politically charged dance music.

search_results.title: About Mia
search_results.snippet: Mia P. Manansala (she/her) is a writer from Chicago who loves books, baking, and bad-ass women. Her debut, ARSENIC AND ADOBO, garnered starred reviews.
